g.text: 2022-12-21 15:38 - Response times to support tickets may be longer during
Christmas and New Years. There will be no response from lunch on Friday 23/12
and morning 27/12, and on 31/12 and 1/1. Merry Christmas!
2022-12-28 09:15 - Next week, on Wednesday January 4th, our sysadmins are
performing the planned cluster maintenance. There will be no feature upgrade in
the DDS this time, but to avoid any issues we will still set the maintenance
mode to active. This means that you will not be able to use the DDS during that
time and any ongoing operations will be cancelled. This maintenance should
overlap with the maintenance at Uppmax.
